Police in Nairobi are investigating an incident where a 42-year-old man allegedly collapsed and died at a lodging in Kawangware on Wednesday. According to a police report on the incident, the deceased; Erastus Madzomba, and his girlfriend of two weeks Elgar Namusia were having a good time at Broadway Lodgings along Thiongo Road. The woman reported that her boyfriend collapsed after they had engaged in sexual intercourse. "Police officers rushed to the scene and found, the body of the deceased lying on the bed in the said room and lodging," reads the report. According to police, the body of the deceased had no visible injuries. The body was moved to city mortuary awaiting postmortem.